ield` is NOT visible (meaning we\'re still on the conversation list because ther
e\'s no conversation), then we should try to create a match first OR just skip t
he sending test.\n\nActually, looking at Maestro docs, there\'s no real conditio
nal branching. The `optional: true` is the only mechanism. The review said:\n- "
