ble conversation_item 失败），则跳过发送测试并标记为 skipped。"\n\nBut Maestro d
oesn\'t have "skip" functionality per se. However, we can make the subsequent st
eps `optional: true` if we can\'t guarantee a conversation exists. But the revie
w explicitly said core steps should NOT be optional.\n\nThe practical solution i
